      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been absolute gold. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-maintained\u2014perfect for anyone who wants a reliable, smooth drive without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019ve loved every mile in this car, and I\u2019m sure you will too! Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
