    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a mechanically sound example of the legendary S54-powered platform. The 3.2L high-revving inline-six features individual throttle bodies and has recently undergone a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and valve clearance adjustment to ensure optimal timing and compression. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory-spec variable M differential lock. The chassis remains rigid, with a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed control arm bushings for precise turn-in. While showing minor aesthetic patina, the performance envelope is intact, offering the linear power delivery and tactile feedback characteristic of this analog era. Riding on staggered alloys with high-performance rubber, this M3 is dialed in for the purist driver.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
