    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2019 BMW 540i xDrive offers a perfect balance of luxury and performance. Finished in a sophisticated Bluestone Metallic, the exterior remains in impressive shape with a deep gloss, showing only minor road wear consistent with careful ownership. Inside, the Mocha Dakota leather interior is pristine; the seats are firm and free of cracks or tears, and the cabin still retains that premium feel. Every feature\u2014from the Harman Kardon surround sound to the gesture-control infotainment\u2014functions exactly as it should. This vehicle has been garage-kept and maintained strictly according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule, with a documented service history available for review. It drives smoothly with plenty of power from the turbocharged inline-six engine and shifts seamlessly through all gears. It\u2019s a reliable, smoke-free, and well-cared-for sedan that is ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
      "price": 34500.0,
